{"type": "article", "id": 23603, "title": "“不完整”的家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-10T07:30:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607185052a60WxDTgAH1QvEY5.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是米兰设计工作室 sovrappensiero 的实验项目，他们想将作品设计成“不完整”的样子。比如桌子的腿并不能维持平衡，需要放上一块石头来维持重力，晾衣架也是如此。另一些物品需要加入配合的物品才有实际的功能，比如花瓶和花，毛巾架和毛巾。它提醒了人们产品和使用者之间的关系，<a href=\"http://www.sovrappensiero.com/work/furnature/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185049bExy9aUBdWsKfl8N.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77261614\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185050HYcMGkIEQvp32JLT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63325183\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185050UrIAQHCjLEk1zslp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.46332518\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px; height: 265px; width: 375px; left: 607px; top: 1002px;\" class=\"dragged\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071850511GJjZ7da3pIU4C5k.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70782396\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185051eJIsVEjf3ZgKyS0u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70293399\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071850519B1lMkbSQuhiJgKj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.22127139\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}